<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <style type="text/css">
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Road+Rage&display=swap');
        #searchbar{ /* Credits to https://github.com/RicardoMarioSonic123 */
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      margin-left: 25%;
      width: 50%;
      height: 6%;
      border-radius: 10000px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      cursor: pointer;
     font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
          font-size: 20.5px;
        }
        .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 3px;
      margin-left: 5px;
      padding: 10.56432px 23px;
      background-color: #060dea;
      color: #ffffff;
      border: 3px solid #2277d8;
      border-radius: 10000px;
      font-weight: 1000;
      cursor: pointer;
     font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;
    }
        .button:hover {
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgb(134, 235, 255),
                /* Glow effect */
                0 0 30px rgb(93, 219, 242);
            /* More intense glow effect */
        }

        .close {
            position: absolute;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 2px 0px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 1.75517px 0.958851px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 1.0806px 1.68294px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 0.141474px 1.99499px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -0.832294px 1.81859px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -1.60229px 1.19694px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -1.97998px 0.28224px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -1.87291px -0.701566px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -1.30729px -1.5136px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) -0.421592px -1.95506px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 0.567324px -1.91785px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 1.41734px -1.41108px 0px, rgb(0, 0, 0) 1.92034px -0.558831px 0px;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding-left: 5px;
            padding-top: 0px;
        }

        #title {  
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: "Road Rage", serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: normal;
        }
    </style>
    <head>
        <!-- <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico"> -->
         <link rel="shortcut icon" href="data:image/x-icon;base64," /><link rel="shortcut icon" href="data:image/x-icon;base64,"/>
        <title>GG on Canvas</title>
    </head>
    <body onload="createArray()" style="margin: 0px; height: 100vh; background-color: black;">
        <div id="texts">
        <h3 id="title">GG on Canvas TEST v0.13 BETA</h3> 
        <h1 style="text-align: center; font: 20px Tahoma, sans-serif; color: white; background: transparent; position: relative;"><span id="dateTime"></span></h1>
        </div>
        <input id='searchbar' onkeyup='search_button()' type='text' name='search' placeholder='Search' autocomplete="off">
        <span class="close" id="closeX" style="display: none;">×</span>
        <iframe id="siteHtml" src="" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0px; border: none; display: none;" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </body>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        function createArray() {
                var sites = [
        {name: "Pixel Shooters (*CRASHES)", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://googleusercontent.b-cdn.net/pixel-shooter/ps.xml&container=ig" },
        {name: "Paper.io 2 (*ADS)", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/bobydob/JSEngine@b8b8a03997f38305098c2f2f5fe14907463cd23b/build/ppo2/ppo2.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Space Huggers", url: "sh"},
        {name: "Survival Race", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://groups.google.com/u/6/group/xd74b-53s-6/attach/3ab53c24b4877/1.xml?part=0.1&view=1&authuser=6&container=ig"},
        {name: "Stock Trading", url: "https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2015-stock-chart-trading-game"},
        {name: "Eggy Car", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://googleusercontent.b-cdn.net/eggy-car/ec.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Space Company", url: "https://mathplayground.us.kg/space-company/index.html"},
        {name: "Slowroads", url: "https://mathplayground.us.kg/slow-roads/index.html"},
        {name: "Snowball.io", url: "data:text/html;base64,"},
        {name: "Final Earth 2", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://529473016-184630684593625815.preview.editmysite.com/uploads/b/139890129-811652923688457694/files/tfe2.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Retro Bowl", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://274079163-174037128449362058.preview.editmysite.com/uploads/b/139890129-899796311729593176/files/rtbl.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Time Shooter 2", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sk1bx/element@1dd0b99d2004b84795f2745a5eb3468deb1c38a4/ts2.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Time Shooter 3", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sk1bx/version@0d8fb9c7430567ed0900902593eee6ba2ba8d297/ts3.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Subway Surfers", url: "https://a6936-19375562.cluster7.canvas-user-content.com/courses/6936~1010708/files/6936~19375562/course%20files/vfcd/index.html"},
        {name: "Idle Breakout", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/bobydob/JSEngine@25ea1da0fd27d58c36d0e4b21ae1e18405ea1244/build/id-br/ibo.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "FNAF", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://s3.amazonaws.com/production-assetsbucket-8ljvyr1xczmb/1ee20621-61bc-4ec8-a8ec-5e839c2e6edc%2Ffive-nights-at-freddy-s.xml&container=ig"},
        {name: "Drive Mad", url: "https://08ff2196-4e28-4c11-b353-e5a6092bb88c.filesusr.com/html/5378fb_2867d10315d432b12b027f91bb6cd0d0.html"},
        {name: "1v1.lol", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://groups.google.com/u/6/group/docs-classroom-s/attach/770f570099aa/go.xml?part=0.1&view=1&container=ig"},
        {name: "Chicken Wars", url: "https://images-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/ifr?url=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/SternyFahizh/RabbitMQ@c56f8a7010e08cba0d629ec7b5570abe2579b0dc/configs%252Frabbitmq/ce.xml&container=ig"}
        ]
        var container = document.createElement("div");
    container.setAttribute("id", "gamesContainer");
    container.id = "siteList"
    document.body.appendChild(container);
    sites.forEach(function(site) {
      var button = document.createElement("button");
      button.textContent = site.name;
      button.className = "button";
      button.onclick = function() {
        // document.body.innerHTML = '<iframe id="' + site.name.replace(/ /g, "") + 'Frame" type="text/html" src="' + site.url + '" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0px; border: none;"></iframe>';
        if (site.url == "sh") {
            document.getElementById("siteHtml").src = "data:text/html;base64,"
        } else {
        document.getElementById("siteHtml").src = site.url
        }
        document.getElementById("siteHtml").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("closeX").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("searchbar").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("siteList").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("texts").style.display = "none";
    };
      container.appendChild(button);
    });
}

        document.getElementById("closeX").onclick = function() {
            document.getElementById("siteHtml").style.display = "none";
            document.getElementById("siteHtml").src = "";
            document.getElementById("closeX").style.display = "none";
            document.getElementById("searchbar").style.display = "inline-block";
            document.getElementById("siteList").style.display = "block";
            document.getElementById("texts").style.display = "block";
        }
        function search_button() {
            let input = document.getElementById('searchbar').value
            input=input.toLowerCase();
            let x = document.getElementsByClassName('button');
            
            for (i = 0; i < x.length; i++) {
                if (!x[i].innerHTML.toLowerCase().includes(input)) {
                    x[i].style.display="none";
                }
                else {
                    x[i].style.display="inline";                
                }
            }
        }
        (function() {
    var days = ['Sunday','Monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday'];
    
    var months = ['January','February','March','April','May','June','July','August','September','October','November','December'];

    Date.prototype.getMonthName = function() {
        return months[ this.getMonth() ];
    };
    Date.prototype.getDayName = function() {
        return days[ this.getDay() ];
    };
})();
var aop = "AM"
    setInterval(updateTime, 1);
function updateTime() {
var now = new Date();
var _day = now.getDayName();
var _month = now.getMonthName();
var h = now.getHours();
var m = now.getMinutes();
var s = now.getSeconds();
// var ms = now.getMilliseconds();
var dayNum = now.getDate();
  if (m < 10) {
    m = "0" + m;
  }
  
  if (s < 10) {
    s = "0" + s;
  }
  
//   if (ms < 100 && ms > 9) {
//     ms = "0" + ms;
//   } else if (ms < 10) {
//     ms = "00" + ms;
//   }
  if (h > 12) {
    aop = "PM"
    h = h - 12;
  } else aop = "AM"
  document.querySelector("#dateTime").textContent = `${_day}, ${_month} ${dayNum} ${h}:${m}:${s} ${aop}`
}
    </script>
</html>
